Usage : echoall <text>
Restricted to immortals only.

Echoall takes the text provided and echos it to every player on the mud.
It will just appear on their screen and your name will not be prepended to
it.

Examples:

echoall Rincewind shouts: Noooooooo!  Stay away from me!

echoall A bolt of lightning strikes down Pinkfish.

echoall The rain is really beginning to get you down.
